{"title":"Help Rockgeist Rebuild Its Shop: Hurricane Helene Relief Shirt","link":"https://theradavist.com/rockgeist-hurricane-helene-relief-shirt/","date":1742907635000,"content":"<p><em>After Hurricane Helene damaged its shop, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/rockgeist/\" target=\"_blank\">Rockgeist</a> is looking to rebuild. To kick off its fundraiser efforts, they’ve released a <a href=\"https://rockgeist.com/product/hurricane-helene-relief-shirt/\" target=\"_blank\">Hurricane Helene Relief shirt</a>…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_08.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_08.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_08.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_08.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_07.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_07.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_07.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_07.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_06.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_06.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_06.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_06.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>100% of the shirt’s proceeds will go to helping the brand get back on its feet. Designed and screen printed in Asheville by Emmy from Rockgeist. Much like the brand’s bags, these shirts are made with care, one at a time.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span><span></span></span><span></span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<p>On September 27th, the French Broad River flooded the Rockgeist workshop with 5 feet of water from Hurricane Helene. The Hurricane brought catastrophic damage across Western North Carolina and other areas of the Southeast. This video is a glimpse into what happened to our workshop and how Rockgeist is rebuilding its business.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_05.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_05.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_05.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The shirt design is linked to Rockgeist’s history:</p>\n<blockquote><p>“We’ve had a print of Katsushika Hokusai’s “Under the Wave off Kanagawa” in the workshop since day one. I found the print in a dumpster outside my Boston apartment when moving to North Carolina. I always thought it depicted what it’s like to run a small business; fighting against the current of larger forces with determination and resolve.</p>\n<p>Emmy took inspiration from Hokusai’s print and created “Helene or Highwater”. Her print carries the same message that I see in the original. It represents our determination to meet the challenges of rebuilding our business. All proceeds will be put towards restarting our workshop in a new location (higher up from the river) and help us get back to making our bags again. Thank you all for contributing to our path forward.”</p></blockquote>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_04.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_04.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_01.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_01.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/03/Rockgeist_Hurrican_Helene_Fundraiser_NC_01.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>If you can, help the brand out by purchasing one of these shirts. Roll on over to Rockgeist to scoop a <a href=\"https://rockgeist.com/product/hurricane-helene-relief-shirt/\" target=\"_blank\">Hurricane Helene Relief Shirt</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/rockgeist-hurricane-helene-relief-shirt/\">Help Rockgeist Rebuild Its Shop: Hurricane Helene Relief Shirt</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"8b731e9a440e16ecff7d293e098aca48cc3d0248f67199d71b94b1e8a0b78773","category":"Cycling"}